    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/f9942fd327d4af149dd66a99178153ad.poster.avif?t=1771406558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/f9942fd327d4af149dd66a99178153ad.webm?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/f9942fd327d4af149dd66a99178153ad.mp4?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在农场改造家游戏中，你将着手改造、扩建以及经营一个成熟发展的美国乡村农场！选项的自由、多样的任务，具有创造性地经营业务和面对各种困境的处理，这些都是此游戏可玩性的重要组成因素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/313b8e599d3827ef503f46d8a5a21fd9.poster.avif?t=1771406558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/313b8e599d3827ef503f46d8a5a21fd9.webm?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/313b8e599d3827ef503f46d8a5a21fd9.mp4?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>改造</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你置身于一个废弃的农场中，尽力把它恢复如初。清除杂草和垃圾、维修破烂的墙面，按照你的喜好刷漆并装饰起来。安放好机器并赋予它们新的生命 - 毫无疑问，它们将在你的农场里派上大用场！购买某些已无法再修理的设备把它们重新拼装起来，收获第一批农作物，并以邀请客户获得资金后进行扩建、进一步改造和提高产量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/949a7793762cdec35bac5009f0755642.poster.avif?t=1771406558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/949a7793762cdec35bac5009f0755642.webm?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/949a7793762cdec35bac5009f0755642.mp4?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩建</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经营管理、投资、成长，以服务于更多的客户。不断扩大你的业务范围。把池塘、果园、牛棚都进行翻新，甚至养蜂场也是？广阔天地中，你会大有作为。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/612b465b5c1d44f75fb308e92208b803.poster.avif?t=1771406558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/612b465b5c1d44f75fb308e92208b803.webm?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/612b465b5c1d44f75fb308e92208b803.mp4?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随心所欲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把农场恢复如初是一回事，在其中打造出你自己的风格又是另一回事。你有多种选择以你的意志来定义周遭的环境。从现有的元素到众多的装饰细节，你可以任意营造出只属于你的独特的氛围。有些装饰品可以较容易地买到，有些则必须在游戏中寻找。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/9efe18837487404a20770789d3e5af68.poster.avif?t=1771406558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/9efe18837487404a20770789d3e5af68.webm?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779610/extras/9efe18837487404a20770789d3e5af68.mp4?t=1771406558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >服务</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >农场的生产工作全面展开后，客户服务将成为你成功的关键一项。做好时间管理、处理事务要有轻重缓急，以及扩大你的服务范围。要多注意产出产品的种类、质量和新鲜度等，不久你肯定会获得进一步发展的资金。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏主要特点：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对一个破旧废弃农场的复原、经营管理以及扩建。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众多可供维修和升级的设施和机器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量可用的装修和装饰的选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种工具供使用。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机事件为游戏增添了多样性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >农作物和牲畜管理选项内容。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供多种服务以满足客户的预期。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以成功为目标的灵活战略选择。</p></li></ul>",
